data.description: Gorgeous recent construction 4 bed, 2.5 bath home in prime Kingwood area location. Discover your dream home! Infused with distinctive charm, this beautifully crafted home stands out by offering an enticing departure from the standard cookie-cutter layouts and design. It offers the perfect blend of modern finishes and comfort. With a thoughtfully designed open floor plan and a range of upgrades, this home is sure to impress.  The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living, dining, and eating areas. Notable upgrades that elevate this home include a 20x12 covered patio, an enlarged primary bath shower with seat, and a cozy corner cast stone fireplace. Additional upgrades include full gutters, premium kitchen cabinets, and flooring. It also has a two-car garage, energy-efficient features, modern curb appeal & a nearly 7,000 sf lot. Woodridge Forest is renowned for its peaceful atmosphere, top-rated schools in the New Caney ISD, and convenient access to shopping, dining, and parks.
